===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of numerous small [[mouselike]], chiefly [[nocturnal]], mammals of the family ''[[Soricidae]]''.
# An ill-tempered, nagging woman: a [[scold]].
#: ''You'd better not stay out late tonight &mdash; your mother is quite a '''shrew''' and you'll never hear the end of it.''

